assy in Israel Vandalized After Polish PM's Controversial Remarks|date=18 February 2018|work=VOA News|accessdate=2021-02-04|archive-date=2018-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180705233207/https://www.voanews.com/a/polish-embassy-in-israel-vandalized-after-polish-pm-controversial-remarks/4260010.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>危机在当年6月下旬得到解决，当时波兰和以色列总理发表了一份联合公报，支持对犹太大屠杀的研究，并谴责“波兰集中营”的说法。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/aponline/2018/06/27/world/europe/ap-eu-poland-holocaust-law-the-latest.html|title=The Latest: Party Head: Israel Confirms Polish View on Nazis|access-date=2018-07-07|language=en|archive-date=2018-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180707143613/https://www.nytimes.com/aponline/2018/06/27/world/europe/ap-eu-poland-holocaust-law-the-latest.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2019年2月，在访问波兰期间，内塔尼亚胡表示，“波兰人与纳粹勾结”，两国关系再次恶化。媒体误引这句话为“波兰人与纳粹勾结”，导致莫拉维基考虑取消原定于下个月前往以色列参加[[维谢格拉德集团|维谢格拉德集团]]峰会的行程。<ref>{{cite news|work=[[Arutz_Sheva|Arutz Sheva]]|title=Polish PM 'seriously considering' cancelling Israel visit|date=15 February 2019|url=https://www.israelnationalnews.com/News/News.aspx/259088?|accessdate=2021-02-04|archive-date=2021-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208121324/https://www.israelnationalnews.com/News/News.aspx/259088|dead-url=no}}</ref>内塔尼亚胡的办公室澄清说，这是《耶路撒冷邮报》错误引用的，他没有说“全体波兰人”，而是“相当数量的波兰人”，波兰政府接受了这个解释。<ref>{{cite news|date=15 February 2018|url=https://www.timesofisrael.com/poland-ends-spat-with-israel-over-pms-comments-blames-media-manipulation/|title=Poland moves to end spat with Israel over PM comments, blames media manipulation|accessdate=2021-02-04|archive-date=2021-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210201200054/https://www.timesofisrael.com/poland-ends-spat-with-israel-over-pms-comments-blames-media-manipulation/|dead-url=no}}</ref>然而，争端在3天后再次燃起，当时以色列外长伊斯雷尔·卡茨声称，“波兰人从他们的母乳中汲取了反犹主义”，随后拒绝道歉，结果导致波兰完全退出了维谢格拉德集团的峰会，导致其最终被取消。<ref>{{cite news|work=[[Jerusalem_Post|Jerusalem Post]]|date=18 February 2019|url=https://www.jpost.com/Israel-News/Anatomy-of-a-crisis-How-Israel-Polish-relations-collapsed-581006|title=ANATOMY OF A CRISIS: HOW ISRAEL-POLISH RELATIONS COLLAPSED|accessdate=2021-02-04|archive-date=2020-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201122105325/https://www.jpost.com/israel-news/anatomy-of-a-crisis-how-israel-polish-relations-collapsed-581006|dead-url=no}}</ref>美国驻波兰大使乔治特·莫斯巴赫表示，以色列不能发表冒犯性言论，<ref>{{Cite news|work=[[Times_of_Israel|Times of Israel]]|date=19 February 2019|title=Siding with Poland, US slams Israeli FM’s ‘offensive’ anti-Semitism remark|url=https://www.timesofisrael.com/siding-with-poland-us-slams-israeli-fms-offensive-anti-semitism-remark/|accessdate=2021-02-04|archive-date=2021-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208034824/https://www.timesofisrael.com/siding-with-poland-us-slams-israeli-fms-offensive-anti-semitism-remark/|dead-url=no}}</ref>并要求以色列道歉。<ref>{{cite news|work=[[Times_of_Israel|Times of Israel]]|date=20 February 2019|title=US envoy calls on FM Katz apologize to Poland for anti-Semitism remark|url=https://www.timesofisrael.com/us-envoy-calls-on-fm-katz-apologize-to-poland-for-anti-semitism-remark/|accessdate=2021-02-04|archive-date=2021-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210201200111/https://www.timesofisrael.com/us-envoy-calls-on-fm-katz-apologize-to-poland-for-anti-semitism-remark/|dead-url=no}}</ref>新任右翼领导人兼内阁部长[[纳夫塔利·贝内特|纳夫塔利·贝内特]]指出，他妻子的家人在波兰的一个森林里生活了四年，最终被波兰人杀害。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.jpost.com/Israel-News/Bennett-on-Poland-We-cannot-allow-anyone-anywhere-to-rewrite-history-580990 |title=Bennett on Poland: We cannot allow anyone, anywhere to rewrite history |accessdate=2021-02-04 |archive-date=2020-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201013173738/https://www.jpost.com/israel-news/bennett-on-poland-we-cannot-allow-anyone-anywhere-to-rewrite-history-580990 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2019年2月，波兰取消了以色列官方代表团对波兰的访问。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.timesofisrael.com/poland-cancels-israeli-delegations-trip-over-holocaust-property-restitution-row/ |title=Poland cancels Israeli officials’ trip over Holocaust property restitution row |accessdate=2021-02-04 |archive-date=2021-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210205104157/https://www.timesofisrael.com/poland-cancels-israeli-delegations-trip-over-holocaust-property-restitution-row/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2019年5月20日，一名男子因向波兰大使马雷克·马杰洛维斯基吐口水而被捕，当时他正坐在大使馆附近的汽车里。这名男子对此表示道歉，并解释说，使馆警卫对他进行的反犹太污蔑让他感到不安。<ref>[https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/.premium-polish-prime-minister-denounces-racist-attack-after-israeli-spits-on-ambassador-1.7243891 Polish President Denounces 'Hate Crime' After Israeli Spits on Ambassador] {{Wayback|url=https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/.premium-polish-prime-minister-denounces-racist-attack-after-israeli-spits-on-ambassador-1.7243891 |date=20201125201852 }}, 15 May 2019, Haaretz</ref>在波兰总理称该事件为“仇外”之后，29名前波兰大使签署了一封信，批评波兰政府的回应。<ref>[https://www.timesofisrael.com/polish-ex-diplomats-say-officials-politicizing-israeli-spitting-incident/ Polish ex-diplomats say Warsaw officials politicizing Israeli spitting incident] {{Wayback|url=https://www.timesofisrael.com/polish-ex-diplomats-say-officials-politicizing-israeli-spitting-incident/ |date=20190526051555 }}, Times of Israel, 19 May 2019</ref>
